# Per-Dockerfile ignore (BuildKit reads <dockerfile-path>.dockerignore first) so
# the bench image build context stays small and never ships host build artifacts
# or the Flutter client into the Linux/arm64 lane. The build context is the repo
# root; only the .NET solution's sources are needed.
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/.vs/
.git/
.github/
publish/
OpenAstroAra.Client/
**/*.user
docs/
design/
*.md
# The bench harness files themselves aren't needed inside the image — the
# Dockerfile is read by the builder, not COPYed, and the test filter is baked
# into the ENTRYPOINT.
bench/
